verses.verse: I will lift <S%H5375>up<s%> my <S%H5869>eyes<s%> unto the <S%H2022>hills<s%>, from from <S%H370>where<s%> <S%H935>comes<s%> my <S%H5828>help<s%>.

He will not <S%H5414>allow<s%> your <S%H7272>foot<s%> to be <S%H4132>moved<s%>: he that <S%H8104>keeps<s%> you will not <S%H5123>slumber<s%>.
<S%H8104>Behold<s%>, he that keeps <S%H3478>Israel<s%> shall neither <S%H5123>slumber<s%> nor <S%H3462>sleep<s%>.
